Quote:  `I want to introduce myself,' I said [to the diggers]. `I'm going to have a service tomorrow .... I hope you will come.' There was a general response: `We'll be there and give you a show,' a bit of diggers' slang, which I found meant -' Here's your chance, can you use it.'
